speech.p: Can I first welcome the furlough extension, as announced by my right hon. Friend the Chancellor, which will give many Carshalton and Wallington residents a great sense of peace of mind? However, some businesses have been in touch with me with concerns about the October cut-off date to be eligible to start furloughing stuff, so can my right hon. Friend outline whether this decision could be reviewed or what other support businesses can access to help mitigate this?
